{"service_name": "RMADS Services", "service_id": "4915044559093760", "company_name": "Evolve Secure Solutions Limited", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Evolve Secure Solutions Limited\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     RMADS Services\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Evolve\u2019s Risk Management &amp; Accreditation Document Set (RMADS) services are tailored by our in-house CLAS team to describe the security specific aspects of a system or service and is the key source of information an Accreditor will use to determine whether assurance requirements are met.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Development of Accreditation Policy\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Preparation of full RMADS\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Review of supplier produced RMADS\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Pragmatic application of HMG risk methodology and bespoke risk approaches\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Delivery of Privacy Impact Assessments (PIAs)\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Scoping and management of penetration testing\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Stakeholder management ensuring consistency of presentation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Proportional value for money approach\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Engagement and communication with accreditor throughout\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Skills transfer and mentoring for internal staff\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Supports system accreditation objectives\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Compliance with Security Policy Framework and HMG IA Standards\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provides supplier assurance through clear documentation of security specific aspects\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Proportional VFM approach matched to risk appetite and data sensitivity\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Tailored to customer requirements to ensure highly focused advice\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Assured quality of delivery by CESG CLAS Consultants\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Reduced cost through pragmatic proportional security and risk control methodology\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Stakeholder confidence that effective security is in place\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Contingency and continuity of service assured by internal CLAS team\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Quality of Service assured by ISO9001, ISO27001, ISO14001, CLAS accreditations\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3800 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92536/4915044559093760-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92536/4915044559093760-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n  